com.guidewire.ab.external.entity

Interface Region

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DecentralizedEntity, Editable, gw.pl.external.entity.Entity, gw.pl.external.entity.KeyableEntity, Retireable, Validatable, Versionable
    Deprecated. 
    External entities are deprecated. Please use the new Java API instead.

    @Deprecated
public interface Region
extends DecentralizedEntity, Retireable, Validatable, gw.pl.external.entity.Entity
    Represents a geographic region, an area of responsibility for a User or Group. A region contains a set of region zones. Regions are therefore heterogenous with respect to a zone type.

        boolean containsZone(Country country,
                   ZoneType zoneType,
                   java.lang.String zone)
        Deprecated. 
        If this region contains a zone of the given type and value? The string matching is case-insensitive NOTE: this will not match if a zip+4 value is provided. You must strip off the +4 before passing to this method.
        Parameters:
        country -
        zoneType - the zone type, must not be null
        zone - the zone string, must not be null
        Returns:
        true if the region containsZone a zone of the given type, false otherwise
